snippet: Stuard shot a 65 at the Sony Open in Honolulu for a one-shot lead over Marc Leishman and Hideto Tanihara going into the weekend.
abstract: Brian Stuard takes second-round lead at the Sony Open golf tournament in Honolulu.
lead_paragraph: Stuard shot a 65 at the Sony Open in Honolulu for a one-shot lead over Marc Leishman and Hideto Tanihara going into the weekend.
